<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَيَصِحُّ النَّفْلُ بِنِيَّةٍ مِنَ النَّهَارِ قَبْلَ الزَّوَالِ وَبَعْدَهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَلَوْ نَوَى إِنْ كَانَ غَداً مِنْ رَمَضَانَ فَهُوَ فَرْضِي:</span> لَمْ يُجْزِئْهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَمَنْ نَوَى الإِفْطَارَ:</span> أَفْطَرَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>* * *<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>